  The old habit of sitting down at a   
 table for a meal with all the family  
 is disappearing because people work or
 like to eat off a tray watching TV.   
  Those people have ready to eat meals,
 or have micro-wave ovens, or other    
 fairly new cookers.                   
  Most leisure is spent at home, either
 watching TV or having a little doze.  
 Most families have 2 children.        
